  "modelText": ["DESCRIPTION:\nThe administration is via a bolus.\nThe PK model has one compartment (volume V) and a Michaelis-Menten elimination (Vm, Km).\n\n[LONGITUDINAL]\ninput = {IFN, Vm, Km, Keff}\n\nIFN = {use=regressor}\n\nEQUATION:\nodeType = stiff\nKap = 0.0153\nBcell_liner_0 = 100\nBcell_Vmax_0 = 100\n\nddt_Bcell_liner = -Kap*(1 - IFN / 10000 * Keff) * Bcell_liner\nddt_Bcell_Vmax = -Kap * (1 - (Vm * IFN) / (Km + IFN)) * Bcell_Vmax\n\nOUTPUT:\noutput = {Bcell_liner, Bcell_Vmax}"]
